}}'''Downdetector'''是一个在线平台，能为用户提供各种网站状态的实时信息。

该网站基于用户的报告來提供应用故障的信息，这些故障报告是该網站通過各种渠道收集而來<ref name="computerworld">{{Cite web|title=Downdetector.com scours Twittersphere to detect service outages faster|url=https://www.computerworld.com/article/2497125/downdetector-com-scours-twittersphere-to-detect-service-outages-faster.html|accessdate=October 28, 2020|author=Miners|date=May 7, 2013|first=Zach|work=[[Computerworld|Computerworld]]|archive-date=2020-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031081527/https://www.computerworld.com/article/2497125/downdetector-com-scours-twittersphere-to-detect-service-outages-faster.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Twitter Down: Users complain that service is suffering outage|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/gadgets-and-tech/twitter-down-outage-social-media-b1057468.html|accessdate=October 28, 2020|date=October 15, 2020|work=[[獨立報|獨立報]]|archive-date=2021-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301105348/https://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/gadgets-and-tech/twitter-down-outage-social-media-b1057468.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。網站還會在地图上显示报告应用故障的位置，地图上方还显示哪些城市有報告故障<ref name="status overview" /><ref>{{Cite web |date=October 15, 2020 |title=Twitter Down: Users complain that service is suffering outage |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/gadgets-and-tech/twitter-down-outage-social-media-b1057468.html |access-date=October 28, 2020 |website=[[The_Independent|The Independent]] |archive-date=2021-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301105348/https://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/gadgets-and-tech/twitter-down-outage-social-media-b1057468.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

Downdetector由Tom Sanders和Sander van de Graaf于2012年4月創辦<ref name="computerworld">{{Cite web|title=Downdetector.com scours Twittersphere to detect service outages faster|url=https://www.computerworld.com/article/2497125/downdetector-com-scours-twittersphere-to-detect-service-outages-faster.html|accessdate=October 28, 2020|author=Miners|date=May 7, 2013|first=Zach|work=[[Computerworld|Computerworld]]}}</ref>。2018年8月<ref>{{Cite web|title=Downdetector is now part of Ookla|url=https://www.speedtest.net/insights/blog/downdetector-announcement/|accessdate=October 28, 2020|date=August 13, 2018|work=[[Speedtest.net|Speedtest.net]]|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109070852/https://www.speedtest.net/insights/blog/downdetector-announcement/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，Downdetector被[[Speedtest.net|Speedtest.net]]的運營方Ookla收购。

